course_title: Advanced Studies in Music Theory - PERIODICITY

sections.comments: A cross-cultural, multi-disciplinary study of rhythm, meter and time in a selection of world music genres, focusing on music theory, analysis and transcription.  With 403D. 2020W Format:  Students attend an online seminar every Tuesday from 1-3:30 pm.

description: Research seminar on a core or emerging topic in music theory. May be repeated to a maximum of 12 credits if different topics are covered.
